{"tid":1591594,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"AFK Arena 25號有大update","createTime":"2019-09-24T08:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T08:27:47.000Z","uid":1647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0424a85c98500bd0458d77a6717bce5d3bc5ed0b","tid":1591594,"uid":1647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">AFK Arena</span></strong></div><br />\n係一隻掛機升呢養老驚，如果想瘋狂沉醉係呢驚度，sorry你可以上一頁<br />\n呢隻驚偏歐美畫風 放置類手機驚，似放置英雄/奇兵玩法<br />\n巴打評價：<br />\n<br />\n唔使肝/平衡好/獎勵多/副本針對大眾<br />\n0課、輕課、中課無大分別，只有極重課可大幅拉開距離<br />\n<br />\n評分都幾高 核心玩法其實都係差不多 但又唔係一成不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.levelwinner.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/afk-arena-best-heroes-guide-800x350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levelwinner.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fafk-arena-best-heroes-guide-800x350.jpg&h=5c010e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.appamped.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/afk-arena-heroes-list-820x451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.appamped.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fafk-arena-heroes-list-820x451.jpg&h=5af5ad23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://mmoraw.com/images/stories/MMO/Android/AFK-Arena/AFK Arena (5).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmmoraw.com%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FMMO%2FAndroid%2FAFK-Arena%2FAFK%20Arena%20%285%29.jpg&h=154ca9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nan: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lilithgame.hgame.gp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.lilithgame.hgame.gp&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=e7b506bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lilithgame.hgame.gp</a><br />\nios: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/afk-arena/id1375425432?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fgb%2Fapp%2Fafk-arena%2Fid1375425432%3Fmt%3D8&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=c12fd263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/afk-arena/id1375425432?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div><br />\n<strong>新手玩家用黎做參考</strong><br />\n歡迎各巴打修改<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/afkp23_img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fafkp23_img.png&h=0cc26fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>首抽:</strong><br />\n呢隻驚無特別要首抽，如果你一定要刷首抽下面有推薦。 <span style=\"color: red;\">只是前期比人好行少少!!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\"> (首十抽必會中一紫)</span><br />\n頭獎:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Brutus_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FBrutus_Ascended.png&h=6bff86cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Shemira_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FShemira_Ascended.png&h=770ef9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Lucius_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FLucius_Ascended.png&h=8926e1d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Tasi_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FTasi_Ascended.png&h=1d53368b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二獎:<br />\n <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Nemora_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FNemora_Ascended.png&h=4af57914&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Fawkes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FFawkes.png&h=f06430a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Eironn_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FEironn_Icon.png&h=8ec63b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/06/Hendrik_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FHendrik_Icon.png&h=29d26ccf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Gorvo_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FGorvo_Icon.png&h=d2456aaa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Baden_Hero_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FBaden_Hero_Icon.png&h=33b1bfd1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Rowan_Icon-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FRowan_Icon-1.png&h=9e4f5183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Lyca_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FLyca_Ascended.png&h=b21e7e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Rosaline_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FRosaline_Icon.png&h=ee0638aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三獎:<br />\n<strong>所有神話級英雄</strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">(圖鑑有寫係咪神話級英雄，所有神話級英雄必定係紫色卡，但係紫卡唔一定係神話級要留意!!!)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Saveas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FSaveas.png&h=621c40fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Hogan_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FHogan_1.png&h=c1973b77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/02/Arden.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FArden.png&h=639ba026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特獎:<span style=\"color: blue;\">(重課金會好勁，0課只夠你去到100lv)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Athalia.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FAthalia.png&h=ec0b490d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Ezizh_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FEzizh_Ascended.png&h=569ccc69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mehira_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FMehira_Icon.png&h=c3dd2545&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Twins_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FTwins_Icon.png&h=e27a0d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前期可以參考<a href=\"https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Ftier-list&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=fcb55327\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.afkarena.net/tier-list</a> 睇下邊隻前期入隊好<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">PS:唔好一開波就睇中期/後期人物評級，你有命過到前期先!!</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">(新出願望清單，可以提高中獎機率)</span><br />\n<br />\n潛力英雄(根據1.22版本調整既後期逆天英雄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Safiya_Icon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FSafiya_Icon.png&h=222ff7d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Kaz_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FKaz_Ascended.png&h=685e7e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.afkarena.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ferael_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FFerael_Ascended.png&h=26a167e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特別<strong>垃圾</strong>獎(中咗喊3聲) <span style=\"color: blue;\">ps:for起手</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/03/Numisu_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FNumisu_Ascended.png&h=22d28441&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/03/Warek_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FWarek_Ascended.png&h=ce0677f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/03/Vurk_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FVurk_Ascended.png&h=83490668&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/03/Skreg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FSkreg.png&h=fef322f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_100,h_100/https://www.afkarena.net/core/uploads/2019/03/Ulmus_Ascended.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fto_webp%2Cq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_100%2Ch_100%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.afkarena.net%2Fcore%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FUlmus_Ascended.png&h=13ac571e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>注意:未過到第五關時唔好係咁問問問邊隻英入唔入隊，因為你根本無英可以換(除非你重課)如果唔係你就跟上面分級表入隊，可以不停試組合，試試下你就知邊隻岩入隊 </strong></span>"}]}